Package: pkgconfig
Title: Private Configuration for 'R' Packages
Version: 2.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gábor", "Csárdi", , "csardi.gabor@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Set configuration options on a per-package basis.  Options
    set by a given package only apply to that package, other packages are
    unaffected.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/r-lib/pkgconfig#readme
